high_descs: Go forward, turn left after the table and go to the other side of the table.
Pick up the knife next to the apple.
Go the left side of the table.
Slice the tomato on the table.
Turn right and go in front of the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the knife on the top shelf.
Turn around and go in front of the table where the tomato is.
Pick up a slice of the tomato.
Turn right and go in front of the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the tomato on the top shelf to the right of the knife, shut the door and then remove the tomato slice.
Go to the right to the end of the room to the microwave.
Put the tomato into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato, put in the fridge and into the microwave.

high_descs: Go around the gray round table on the left to the other side.
Pick up the gray knife in front of the white mug.
Go around to be near the tomato on the gray round table.
Slice the tomato on the table.
Go right to the front of the refrigerator.
Place the knife on the top shelf in the refrigerator.
Turn around to go back to the round table.
Pick up one slice of the tomato.
Go back to the refrigerator.
Chill the tomato slice on the right of the knife in the refrigerator. and take it out.
Go left to the counter with the microwave on top across the kitchen.
Place the tomato slice next to the white mug in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Go to the round black table
Pick up the knife
Go to the middle of the table
Cut the tomato on the table
Go to the fridge
Put the knife in the fridge
Go to the black table
Pick up a tomato slice
Go to the fridge
Chill the tomato
Go to the microwave
Put the tomato slice in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled slice of tomato in the microwave
